{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Tax credits - your payment dates"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/when-is-your-next-tax-credits-payment.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/when-is-your-next-tax-credits-payment"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"2052","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"When are your tax credit payments due and how bank holidays affect your payments","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:14:26+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Your payments are made every week or every 4 weeks - they\u2019re paid early if the payment date is a bank holiday.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You choose how often you want to be paid on your claim form. </p>\n\n<p>Your award notice tells you the date of your first payment. You can use this or your bank statements to work out when your next payment is due. </p>\n\n<h2>Bank holidays</h2>\n\n<p>Your payment is paid early if it&rsquo;s due on <strong>any</strong> UK bank holiday. </p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Bank holiday</th>\n      <th>Payment date</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>6 Aug 2012 (Scotland only)</td>\n      <td>3 Aug 2012</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>27 Aug 2012 (summer bank holiday)</td>\n      <td>24 Aug 2012</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>30 Nov 2012 (St Andrew&rsquo;s Day - Scotland)</td>\n      <td>29 Nov 2012</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>25 Dec 2012 (Christmas Day)</td>\n      <td>24 Dec 2012</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>26 Dec 2012 (Boxing Day)</td>\n      <td>24 Dec 2012</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>27 Dec 2012 (Northern Ireland)</td>\n      <td>24 Dec 2012</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Check your bank account and then call the <a href=\"/contact-the-tax-credit-office\" title=\"Contact the Tax Credit Office\">Tax Credit Office</a> if your payment is late.</p>\n</div>\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Tax credits","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/benefits%2Ftax-credits.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes working tax credit, child tax credit and when tax credits stop","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=benefits%2Ftax-credits","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/benefits/tax-credits"},"parent":{"title":"Benefits","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/benefits.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Eligibility and how to apply","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=benefits","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/benefits"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Tax credits calculator","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tax-credits-calculator.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/tax-credits-calculator","format":"transaction","details":{"need_id":"696","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Renew your tax credits","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/renewing-your-tax-credits-claim.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/renewing-your-tax-credits-claim","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":null,"business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Tax credits overpayments","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tax-credits-overpayments.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/tax-credits-overpayments","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"688","business_proposition":false}}]]],"parts":null}